Dimensions

  • View in centimeters
  • View in inches
  • Sample Swatch Size:
  • Dimensions: 26 in. x 4.5 ft.
  • Covers: 9.75 sq. ft.
  • Usable Fabric Width:
  • Repeat Type: Straight
  • Repeat Size: 27 in. x 27 in.
  • Overprint: 1/4” bleed on width, 1/2" bleed on length, trimmed. The overprint provides panels extra protection when shipping, and additional wiggle-room for installation. The overprint can stay on the panel or it can be cut off prior to installation.
  • Material: Removable paper with removable pressure sensitive adhesive backing.
  • Application Method: Easy peel and stick application. See how to install a removable panel.
Made to order; non-refundable. See more information on shipping and returns.

DESIGNER SHOWCASE

Why we collaborated on this collection with this artist!

'Cactus' Wallpaper by Tea Collection - Persimmon
  • Digitally-printed on 100% nontoxic eco friendly paper
  • Material: bright smooth matte finish, scratch resistant paper
  • Made to order; non-refundable
  • Sustainably made in Los Angeles, CA

Our standard lead-time for wallpaper orders is 14-21 business days to produce however we may be able to offer rush production services. Rush production is 5-7 business days with a 50% surcharge.

Please contact us prior to placing your order to confirm.

Note: All orders are shipped from our headquarters in California. We use FedEx/UPS ground however you can select expedited shipping services at check out.

SECTION TAGLINE

How to Install ?

Learn More Learn More

1.

Prep the wall

Fill in old nail holes and blemishes, and smooth out any rough areas. After, clean the walls to remove dirt and dust, leaving a clean surface for the wallpapers

Learn More Learn More

2.

Trim the panels

Trim off any excess wallpaper with the utility knife in order to align it properly on the wall you want.

Learn More Learn More

3.

Align and Install

Rub the wallpaper with a soft cloth or sponge to ensure it is securely attached to the wall. Continue with the next panel using the same techniques.

Learn More Learn More
